{"type":"message","id":"70a02f04","parentId":"0e06809a","timestamp":"2026-02-15T11:01:57.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Incorporating the Graph**\n\nI'm inserting the clean dependency graph for the trading module into `SYSTEM_FLOW.md`. It'll be \"Section 3\". After appending it, I'll consider that task complete.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771153317580_352","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\n## 3. Trading Module Dependency Graph (Generated)\n\nThis graph shows the internal dependencies of the core trading logic.\n\n```mermaid\nclassDiagram\n  class trading {\n  }\n  class advanced_strategies {\n  }\n  class backtester {\n  }\n  class engine {\n  }\n  class fees {\n  }\n  class regime_detector {\n  }\n  class strategies {\n  }\n  class base {\n  }\n  class cs2 {\n  }\n  class dota2 {\n  }\n  class rust {\n  }\n  class tf2 {\n  }\n  class trading_automation {\n  }\n  trading --> backtester\n  trading --> regime_detector\n  trading --> trading_automation\n  advanced_strategies --> regime_detector\n  engine --> fees\n  strategies --> base\n  strategies --> cs2\n  strategies --> dota2\n  strategies --> rust\n  strategies --> tf2\n  base --> fees\n  cs2 --> base\n  dota2 --> base\n  rust --> base\n  tf2 --> base\n```\n","file_path":"D:\\Dmarket_bot\\docs_archive\\SYSTEM_FLOW.md"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":37954,"output":324,"cacheRead":37129,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38278,"cost":{"input":0.075908,"output":0.003888,"cacheRead":0.007425800000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0872218}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771153312132}}
